title: AVTECH Room Alert 3S: Sensor Voltage
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/avtech
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the voltage of sensors
 connected to a AVTECH Room Alert 3S device.
 Upper levels can be configured via the _Voltage levels_ ruleset.

item:
 "Voltage Sensor" if the connected sensor is a voltage sensor.

discovery:
 One service is created if the sensor emits voltage data.
